     H            Y.
     F** ACHR01 *********************************************
     F*調整理由ファイルの更新                             *
     F*       ITS.                 2012.04.25               *
     F*かんばんマスターの更新からCALLされるが           *
     F*更新対象のかんばんマスターはレコードロックが       *
     F*かかっている為、ワークファイルに出力しておき       *
     F*更新プログラムの後、ACHR09で                     *
     F*かんばんマスターに更新をかける                     *
     F*
%0001F* SAKAKI 2020.07.29 PSTS = '1'を追加（自動調整）    *
     F* 2021.01.20 DCS. T.MITSUI
     F*   CHANGE WITH THE NUMBER OF FIGURES EXPANSION OF THE "KANBAN"
     F*******************************************************
     FACHPW01 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FABHPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FADHPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FAKBPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FACHWP01 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     E                    ER      1  20 65               d[- xlﾈ-ﾆﾞ
      * ACHWP01
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80Z1KOHZ
     I                                        1   40Z1KOYY
     I                                        5   60Z1KOMM
     I                                        7   80Z1KODD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60Z1KOTM
     I                                        1   40Z1KOT4
     I                                        1   20Z1KOHH
     I                                        3   40Z1KOSS
     I                                        5   60Z1KOMN
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                        1  10 PGMNM
     I                                       91 170 MSGTXT
     I                                      244 253 WSID
     I                                      254 263 USID
     I                                      264 269 JBNO
     I*システム値
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60WTIME
     I                                        1   20SYSJI
     I                                        3   40SYSPN
     I                                        5   60SYSBY
      *
     I              'KANBAN ADJUST'       C         CMT01
      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  パラメータＴＲＡＮＣＦＥＲ                      *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@JBN1  1
     C                     PARM           P@JBN2  2
     C                     PARM           P@JBN3  2
     C                     PARM           P@JBN4  1
     C                     PARM           P@UKYY  40
     C                     PARM           P@UKMM  20
     C                     PARM           P@UKDD  20
     C                     PARM           P@UBIN  20
     C                     PARM           P@FPGM 10
     C                     PARM           P@MAIS  50       調整枚数
      * ' ' = UPDATE
      * '1' = AUTO ADJUST
      * 'M' = INQUIRY
     C                     PARM           PSTS    1        *ステータス
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  メインルーチン                                  *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     MOVE PSTS      W@SYS   1
      *
     C                     EXSR #SB100
     C           DSPSW     DOWNE'99'
     C                     EXSR #SB200
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   初期処理                                       *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB100    BEGSR
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     MOVE P@JBN1    K@JBN1  1
     C                     MOVE P@JBN2    K@JBN2  2
     C                     MOVE P@JBN3    K@JBN3  2
     C                     MOVE P@JBN4    K@JBN4  1
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKYY    K@UKYY  40
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKMM    K@UKMM  20
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKDD    K@UKDD  20
     C                     Z-ADDP@UBIN    K@UBIN  20
     C                     MOVE WSID      E@JOBM 10
     C                     MOVE USID      E@USER 10
     C                     MOVE JBNO      E@WNBR  6
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     E@DATE  80
      *
     C           E@KKEY    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN1
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN2
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN3
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN4
     C                     KFLD           K@UKYY
     C                     KFLD           K@UKMM
     C                     KFLD           K@UKDD
     C                     KFLD           K@UBIN
      *
     C           E@KKEY    CHAINABHPL031             54
     C           *IN54     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR #ABH
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           E@KKEY    CHAINADHPL031             54
     C           *IN54     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR #ADH
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           E@KKEY    CHAINAKBPL031             54
     C           *IN54     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR #AKB
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           KEYZ11    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN1
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN2
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN3
     C                     KFLD           K@JBN4
     C                     KFLD           K@UKYY
     C                     KFLD           K@UKMM
     C                     KFLD           K@UKDD
     C                     KFLD           K@UBIN
     C                     KFLD           E@JOBM 10
     C                     KFLD           E@USER 10
     C                     KFLD           E@WNBR  6
     C                     KFLD           E@DATE  80
      *
     C           KEYZ11    CHAINACHWP011             88
     C           *IN88     IFEQ '0'
     C                     EXSR #ANZ                       GET WORK
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           W@SYS     IFEQ 'M'
     C                     SETON                     43    PROTECT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     Z-ADDP@MAIS    D1MAIS
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1DAND    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1KYOT    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1FRYO    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1SENY    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D11NAI    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D12NAI    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1JISK    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1AUAJ    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1OTHH    D1CMAI
%0001 * AUTO ADJUST
%0001C           W@SYS     IFEQ '1'
%0001C                     EXSR #SB500
%0001C                     MOVEL'99'      DSPSW
      *
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVEL'01'      DSPSW   2
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB100    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   主処理                                         *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB200    BEGSR
      *
     C           DSPSW     DOWEQ'01'
     C                     EXSR #SB210
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR         ESB200    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   詳細画面処理                                   *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB210    BEGSR
     C                     EXFMTACHPW011
      *
     C                     SETOF                     313233
     C                     SETOF                     343536
     C                     SETOF                     373839
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C                     SETOF                     4142
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D1ERR
      * F3
     C           *IN03     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE '99'      DSPSW
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           W@SYS     IFEQ 'M'
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
      *更新チェック
     C                     EXSR #SB400
      *
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '1'
     C                     GOTO ESB210
     C                     ENDIF
      * F5
     C           *IN05     IFEQ '1'
     C                     EXSR #FILE
     C                     MOVE '99'      DSPSW
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         ESB210    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *            更新時画面チェック処理                *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     C           #SB400    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1DAND    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1KYOT    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1FRYO    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1SENY    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D11NAI    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D12NAI    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1JISK    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1AUAJ    D1CMAI
     C                     ADD  D1OTHH    D1CMAI
      *
     C           D1CMAI    IFNE D1MAIS
     C                     SETON                     313233
     C                     SETON                     343999
     C                     SETON                     353637
     C                     MOVELER,1      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO ESB400
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           D1OTHH    IFNE 0
     C           D1CMT1    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           D1CMT2    ANDEQ*BLANK
     C                     SETON                     414299
     C                     MOVELER,2      D1ERR
     C                     GOTO ESB400
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           ESB400    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *ワークファイル更新処理                            *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #FILE     BEGSR
      *
     C           KEYZ11    CHAINACHWP011             88
     C                     MOVELWSID      Z1JOBM
     C                     MOVELUSID      Z1USER
     C                     MOVELJBNO      Z1WNBR
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     Z1DATE
     C                     MOVELP@FPGM    Z1FPGM
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     Z1KOHZ
     C                     TIME           Z1KOTM
     C                     MOVELUSID      Z1KOME
     C                     MOVELPGMNM     Z1KOPG
      *
     C                     MOVELP@JBN1    Z1JBN1
     C                     MOVELP@JBN2    Z1JBN2
     C                     MOVELP@JBN3    Z1JBN3
     C                     MOVELP@JBN4    Z1JBN4
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKYY    Z1UKYY
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKMM    Z1UKMM
     C                     Z-ADDP@UKDD    Z1UKDD
     C                     Z-ADDP@UBIN    Z1UBIN
      *
     C                     Z-ADDD1CMAI    Z1CMAI
     C                     Z-ADDD1DAND    Z1DAND
     C                     Z-ADDD1KYOT    Z1KYOT
     C                     Z-ADDD1FRYO    Z1FRYO
     C                     Z-ADDD1SENY    Z1SENY
     C                     Z-ADDD11NAI    Z11NAI
     C                     Z-ADDD12NAI    Z12NAI
     C                     Z-ADDD1JISK    Z1JISK
     C                     Z-ADDD1AUAJ    Z1AUAJ
     C                     Z-ADDD1OTHH    Z1OTHH
     C                     MOVELD1CMT1    Z1CMT1
     C                     MOVELD1CMT2    Z1CMT2
      *
     C           *IN88     IFEQ '0'
     C                     UPDATACHWP011
     C                     ELSE
     C                     WRITEACHWP011
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     CSR         EFILE     ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * ABHPV06                                            *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #ABH      BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADDM6KOHZ    D1KOHZ
     C                     MOVELM6KMEI    D1KOME
     C                     MOVELM6HIN1    D1SHN1
     C                     MOVELM6HIN2    D1SHN2
     C                     MOVELM6HIN3    D1SHN3
      *
     C                     Z-ADDM6CMAI    D1CMAI
     C                     Z-ADDM6DAND    D1DAND
     C                     Z-ADDM6KYOT    D1KYOT
     C                     Z-ADDM6FRYO    D1FRYO
     C                     Z-ADDM6SENY    D1SENY
     C                     Z-ADDM61NAI    D11NAI
     C                     Z-ADDM62NAI    D12NAI
     C                     Z-ADDM6JISK    D1JISK
     C                     Z-ADDM6AUAJ    D1AUAJ
     C                     Z-ADDM6OTHH    D1OTHH
     C                     MOVELM6CMT1    D1CMT1
     C                     MOVELM6CMT2    D1CMT2
      *
     CSR         EABH      ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * ADHPV06                                            *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #ADH      BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADDJ6KOHZ    D1KOHZ
     C                     MOVELJ6KOME    D1KOME
     C                     MOVELJ6SHN1    D1SHN1
     C                     MOVELJ6SHN2    D1SHN2
     C                     MOVELJ6SHN3    D1SHN3
      *
     C                     Z-ADDJ6CMAI    D1CMAI
     C                     Z-ADDJ6DAND    D1DAND
     C                     Z-ADDJ6KYOT    D1KYOT
     C                     Z-ADDJ6FRYO    D1FRYO
     C                     Z-ADDJ6SENY    D1SENY
     C                     Z-ADDJ61NAI    D11NAI
     C                     Z-ADDJ62NAI    D12NAI
